'''''Doc the Destroyer''''' is a [[1987 in video gaming|1987]] [[role-playing video game]] for the [[Commodore 64]] and [[ZX Spectrum]]. It was published in the [[United Kingdom]] by [[Krome Studios Melbourne|Melbourne House]]. The game offers [[computer keyboard|keyboard]] or [[joystick]] input for [[multiple choice]] adventure.

== Plot ==

The story follows Doc, a [[time travel]]ler. As Doc is searching for adventure by traveling to different time periods, he stops in Domed City. Doc thinks he'll find some adventure here, but somehow loses his [[time travel|time machine]] and can't escape from this era. You make decisions for Doc as you help find his long lost machine.<ref name=ZAP/>

